Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.10,0:01:33.02,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur3}And feel, feel a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.50,0:01:41.52,OP_JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(160,160)\blur3}感じるままに生きてゆけたら
